sentences: Petter Vågan  (born 6 July 1982 in Brønnøysund, Northern Norway) is a Norwegian singer, guitarist, composer, and the younger brother of double bass player Ole Morten Vågan.
He is the bandleader, singer, and guitarist of the Norwegian indie electronica band The Fjords, founded in 2013.
2013: Rendition of a Whisper (Gigafon), Petter O Hanna
